Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来雨快停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了 我还在担心雨停不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么就再等一会儿吧 直到雨停为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.71,0:01:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黄金假期也结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一放完假就要期中考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.65,0:01:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过在这之前要先选学生会会长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹井会长说务必要请你接任下一届的会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.73,0:02:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然还是不想当吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.17,0:02:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 那个人…其他人也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不知道他在期待些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.31,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然会错意了 我实在很困扰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实真正的我是更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.43,0:02:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨这么大你在这里干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这句话应该我说才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身都淋湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你该不会又迷路了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我在找东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.78,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.98,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在找这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！真是可爱的小猫咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道她会这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 她是老虎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 老虎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩杞纱 是只老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.63,0:03:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说老虎就是十二生肖的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十二生肖的老虎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面 我叫本田透…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.57,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀 被咬了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 好好跟小透道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.69,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 小纱不会说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.27,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上国中后没多久就突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟说她是得了心病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愿意把话说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从此就再也没说过话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成逃学的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天终于…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翘家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我四处找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.83,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到时 已经变成一只老虎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为被异性碰到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 好像只是身体太虚弱的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.34,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是为了什么原因才变成这样的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被欺负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛啊 怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你生气了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪我多嘴是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要搞清楚 我们有多担心你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸妈现在正四处在找你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 泼春你流血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.38,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下落不明的杞纱…止血…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你冷静点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.52,0:05:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我去帮杞纱止血…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是紫吴你过度冷静吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春 你刚刚是不是"变黑"了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 就算很痛也只能生闷气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱那家伙真拿她没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 你在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 你在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是一点也不痛…对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.17,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还是有点痛又有点不痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之我们先回家吧 杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 我是妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是紫吴专程打电话给妈妈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.92,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老给周遭的人添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在干什么 到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让妈妈感到困扰真的这么有趣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.97,0:06:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于拥有被怪物附身小孩的母亲们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.84,0:06:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是过度保护孩子就是排斥他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.72,0:06:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何不说在学校被欺负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何要离家出走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何什么都不说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.13,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她可能是说不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.74,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一想到妈妈知道真相后会有什么反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.62,0:07:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想让人知道这样的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命虚张声势想掩饰这一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让自己更觉得没出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更觉得丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.72,0:07:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定妈妈也很讨厌这个被人欺负的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人不断在想这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断想这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以更是说不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最担心害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最难过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是被自己最喜欢的人讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寄住？你说杞纱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为种种原因 暂时把她接来这里住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么种种原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就别追问了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.51,0:09:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看她妈妈也快不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就当作是在复建吧 先让她们暂时分开一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听得雾煞煞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱到底跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧黏着小透不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱寄住在这里 经过了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说真的连上厕所都等 我实在觉得不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人感到不可思议的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这三天里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱对我是寸步不离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.69,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换句话说 就是她还蛮喜欢我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点像刚在学走路的小女娃 感觉挺温馨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会觉得厌烦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会嫌烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的是…超爱你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像很开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在搞不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 我肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我马上做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 你今晚想吃什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 你连自己想吃什么都不会说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨～\N喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于这个既笨又蠢的阿夹所说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就别放在心上吧 小纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 别爬到我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别摸我 真恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.25,0:11:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 还是不愿意开口说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 我想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走迷宫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 用走迷宫来决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.29,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 杞纱你喜欢走哪条路线呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一条吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我要开始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么歌呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚要吃韭菜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亏你说得出口 你真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.72,0:12:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？啊！我不是那个意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.75,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这该怎说好呢 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就给我用心点煮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讨厌 为了这么点小事拌嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道什么叫拌嘴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.47,0:12:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱迟早一定能用她那可爱的声音跟我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 也不能老住在紫吴家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱今后该如何是好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是想这种问题的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为她的个性认真 常想些不该想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会把自己逼到那种窘境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有她妈妈也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱的妈妈已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她昨天打电话来道谢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.64,0:13:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱她还好吗 三餐都有吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.11,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱不喜欢干干的东西 她爱吃韭菜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.52,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…那是杞纱的妈妈还是很爱杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说的没错吧 否则根本不会打电话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说的没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过话说回来 杞纱为何会被欺负呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.34,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我听到伯母们的谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为杞纱绝不肯告诉我原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 刚开始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.52,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都说看不顺眼她的头发跟眼睛颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛色不同的怪家伙被排斥是她的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是被说得很难听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.07,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说你的人不是都被你K得很惨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比阿夹好一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙把人打得剩下半条命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过呢 杞纱也尽了努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她告诉大家这个毛色是天生的她也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果大家开始对她视而不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不仅对她视而不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每当杞纱一说什么大家就嘲笑她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说会窃窃地嘲笑她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.11,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我呢 在我班上从没人对我这样过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我只能凭空想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想像过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.62,0:15:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每当我说话时 大家都会在一旁窃笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那会是什么样的感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是非常…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲哀的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被嘲笑的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后会变得愈来愈懦弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变得什么话都不敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.48,0:15:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算明知周围的人会很着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是眼前却是一片黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吸愈来愈困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内心也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,语言就这么死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要上课了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:16:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 我今天要去紫吴老师那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便有东西要给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有东西给她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.28,0:16:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信 杞纱的导师寄来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内容可能让人看了会想吐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不觉得变软弱是件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不觉得坚强就是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说这是个弱肉强食的社会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我们并非动物 我们是人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.74,0:16:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为十二生肖的我们也是人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.88,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,写了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学 近况可好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多该来学校了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班上的同学们也都在等草摩同学来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有任何问题可以找老师商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你能积极的加入这个团体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一来就会发现最重要的事就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学必须先学着喜欢自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.13,0:17:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出自己的优点 喜欢上自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.17,0:17:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想想 连自己都讨厌自己 别人又怎么会喜欢你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.82,0:17:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是超恶心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.09,0:18:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么叫做喜欢自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的优点该从何找起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只知道自己的缺点是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为不知道才讨厌自己的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当有人说喜欢自己时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.22,0:18:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是自己开始喜欢上自己的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当有人肯接纳自己时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.56,0:18:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得自己也就能开始原谅及喜欢自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都非常喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…也只能这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.33,0:19:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们能做的只有喜欢你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.12,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久没听到你的声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.75,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说起话虽然还有点结巴的杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然说要去上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.53,0:20:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老实说 对于杞纱的离开 我还真是有点不舍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.88,0:20:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果继续这么下去 情况可能会更糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不能跟大家合好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续被大家无视于我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.39,0:20:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱正打算鼓起勇气勇于面对问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希也一起来就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说还有重要的事要办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚刚说什么
